---
(command (word "echo") (word "$[$x]"))
---


=== variable in expression
echo $[x+1]
---
(command (word "echo") (word "$[x+1]"))
---


=== multiple variables
echo $[a+b]
---
(command (word "echo") (word "$[a+b]"))
---


=== parenthesized expression
